{"root":{"data":{"id":"d40pof50pi00","created":1725779225152,"text":"Linux网络设备驱动"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d40poz78s0w0","created":1725779268822,"text":"嵌入式网络硬件","progress":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d40ppliii9s0","created":1725779317393,"text":"MAC（Media Access Control，媒体访问控制）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d40pra7qo7s0","created":1725779449525,"text":"SOC内部集成，通过MAC连接外部独立的PHY芯片"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d40pvmfe9zs0","created":1725779789566,"text":"特点：网速较高，因为由专门用于网络处理的DMA"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d40pwi7nzu00","created":1725779858756,"text":"MAC和PHY之间进行网络数据传输"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d40q0b7kb3s0","created":1725780156969,"text":"MII（Media Identical Interface，介质独立接口）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d40q0fssc400","created":1725780166959,"text":"RMII（Reduced MII，简化介质独立接口）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d40pzc5313c0","created":1725780080631,"text":"MAC读取PHY的内部寄存器，对PHY进行配置"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d40q0x47wv40","created":1725780204656,"text":"MDIO（Management Data Input/Output，管理数据输入输出）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d40q101iw5s0","created":1725780211023,"text":"MDC（Management Data Clock，管理数据时钟）"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d40prb584yo0","created":1725779451550,"text":"独立芯片，在SOC外部，通常为MAC+PHY的形式"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d40pupsd4cw0","created":1725779718516,"text":"特点：网速不高"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d40pt2itty80","created":1725779589510,"text":"三星的开发板通常外置一个DM9000，DM9000给SOC提供一个SRAM接口，SOC以操控SRAM的形式来操控网卡芯片"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d40pu5w97xs0","created":1725779675216,"text":"W5500芯片内置了硬件TCP/IP协议，向SOC提供SPI接口"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d40ppp5wg480","created":1725779325337,"text":"PHY（Physical Layer，物理层）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d40pydra7fk0","created":1725780005786,"text":"PHY芯片通常与RJ45接口（网线接口）相连，通过网线实现与其他网络设备的连接。在连接过程中，可能需要使用网络变压器来增强信号和隔离外部设备。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d40pyhiun1c0","created":1725780013984,"text":"MAC负责数据的封装和解析，而PHY负责数据的实际发送和接收。"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"classic","version":"1.4.43"}